    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Relatively small knives having a short, curved blade; used in interior construction and crafts. Used primarily for cutting linoleum, sheets of veneer, vinyl, heavy paper board, carpeting, and other moderately flexible materials of similar weight.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
